FORMAT: 1A
HOST: http://localhost:3000/api/v1

# Book Management API

CRUD API for managing books.

## Books Collection [/books]

### List all books [GET]
+ Parameters
    + category (string, optional) - Filter by category
    + limit (number, optional) - Max results
    + offset (number, optional) - Skip results

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Body
            {
              "books": [
                {"id": "1", "title": "The Great Gatsby", "author": "F. Scott Fitzgerald", "isbn": "978-0-7432-7356-5", "publishYear": 1925, "price": 10.99, "category": "Classic"}
              ],
              "total": 1
            }

### Create a new book [POST]
+ Request (application/json)
    + Body
            {
              "title": "The Great Gatsby",
              "author": "F. Scott Fitzgerald",
              "isbn": "978-0-7432-7356-5",
              "publishYear": 1925,
              "price": 10.99,
              "category": "Classic"
            }

+ Response 201 (application/json)
    + Body
            {
              "id": "1",
              "title": "The Great Gatsby",
              "author": "F. Scott Fitzgerald",
              "isbn": "978-0-7432-7356-5",
              "publishYear": 1925,
              "price": 10.99,
              "category": "Classic"
            }

## Book Resource [/books/{id}]

### Get book by ID [GET]
+ Parameters
    + id (string, required) - Book ID

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Body
            {
              "id": "1",
              "title": "The Great Gatsby",
              "author": "F. Scott Fitzgerald",
              "isbn": "978-0-7432-7356-5",
              "publishYear": 1925,
              "price": 10.99,
              "category": "Classic"
            }

### Update book [PUT]
+ Parameters
    + id (string, required) - Book ID

+ Request (application/json)
    + Body
            {
              "title": "The Great Gatsby (Revised)",
              "price": 12.99
            }

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Body
            {
              "id": "1",
              "title": "The Great Gatsby (Revised)",
              "author": "F. Scott Fitzgerald",
              "isbn": "978-0-7432-7356-5",
              "publishYear": 1925,
              "price": 12.99,
              "category": "Classic"
            }

### Delete book [DELETE]
+ Parameters
    + id (string, required) - Book ID

+ Response 204
